#. <section class="sutta" id="sn40.4"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn40.4:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 40"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 40"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn40.4:0.2"
msgid "1. Moggallānavagga"
msgstr "1. By Moggallāna"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 4. Catutthajhānapañhāsutta → upekkhāsuttaṃ (bj) | upekkhako (pts1)
msgctxt "sn40.4:0.3"
msgid "4. Catutthajhānapañhāsutta"
msgstr "4. A Question About the Fourth Absorption"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn40.4:1.1"
msgid "“‘Catutthaṃ jhānaṃ, catutthaṃ jhānan’ti vuccati."
msgstr "“They speak of this thing called the ‘fourth absorption’."

msgctxt "sn40.4:1.2"
msgid "Katamaṃ nu kho catutthaṃ jhānanti?"
msgstr "What is the fourth absorption?"

msgctxt "sn40.4:1.3"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, āvuso, etadahosi:"
msgstr "It occurred to me:"

msgctxt "sn40.4:1.4"
msgid ""
"‘idha bhikkhu sukhassa ca pahānā dukkhassa ca pahānā pubbeva "
"somanassadomanassānaṃ atthaṅgamā adukkhamasukhaṃ upekkhāsatipārisuddhiṃ "
"catutthaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati."
msgstr ""
"‘It’s when, giving up pleasure and pain, and ending former happiness and "
"sadness, a mendicant enters and remains in the fourth absorption, without "
"pleasure or pain, with pure equanimity and mindfulness."

msgctxt "sn40.4:1.5"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati catutthaṃ jhānan’ti."
msgstr "This is called the fourth absorption.’"

msgctxt "sn40.4:1.6"
msgid ""
"So khvāhaṃ, āvuso, sukhassa ca pahānā dukkhassa ca pahānā pubbeva "
"somanassadomanassānaṃ atthaṅgamā adukkhamasukhaṃ upekkhāsatipārisuddhiṃ "
"catutthaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharāmi."
msgstr "And so … I was entering and remaining in the fourth absorption."

msgctxt "sn40.4:1.7"
msgid ""
"Tassa mayhaṃ, āvuso, iminā vihārena viharato sukhasahagatā saññāmanasikārā "
"samudācaranti."
msgstr ""
"While I was in that meditation, perceptions and attentions accompanied by "
"pleasure beset me."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli4.266"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn40.4:2.1"
msgid "Atha kho maṃ, āvuso, bhagavā iddhiyā upasaṅkamitvā etadavoca:"
msgstr "Then the Buddha came up to me with his psychic power and said:"

msgctxt "sn40.4:2.2"
msgid "‘moggallāna, moggallāna."
msgstr "‘Moggallāna, Moggallāna!"

msgctxt "sn40.4:2.3"
msgid ""
"Mā, brāhmaṇa, catutthaṃ jhānaṃ pamādo, catutthe jhāne cittaṃ saṇṭhapehi, "
"catutthe jhāne cittaṃ ekodiṃ karohi, catutthe jhāne cittaṃ samādahā’ti."
msgstr ""
"Don’t neglect the fourth absorption, brahmin! Settle your mind in the fourth "
"absorption; unify your mind and immerse it in the fourth absorption.’"

msgctxt "sn40.4:2.4"
msgid ""
"So khvāhaṃ, āvuso, aparena samayena sukhassa ca pahānā dukkhassa ca pahānā "
"pubbeva somanassadomanassānaṃ atthaṅgamā adukkhamasukhaṃ "
"upekkhāsatipārisuddhiṃ catutthaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja vihāsiṃ."
msgstr ""
"And so, after some time … I entered and remained in the fourth absorption."

msgctxt "sn40.4:2.5"
msgid "Yañhi taṃ, āvuso, sammā vadamāno vadeyya … pe … mahābhiññataṃ patto”ti."
msgstr ""
"So if anyone should be rightly called a disciple who attained to great "
"direct knowledge with help from the Teacher, it’s me.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn40.4:2.6"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
